{"tid":792051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★風雨中營救核潛艇平台　3專家被浪吞噬亡","createTime":"2018-08-24T09:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:20:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc77605c778558bc0ed6b22d42a0d83e690c3d9f","tid":792051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"遼寧大連周一（20日）因受颱風「溫比亞」影響，刮起狂風暴雨，當天上午10時左右，停泊在中船重工第760研究所南碼頭的一個國家重點試驗平台出現險情，研究所副所長黃群等3名專家因搶險而被巨浪吞噬，最終墮海溺亡。事發片段曝光，可見當時共有12名工作人員冒着風雨，試圖加固平台的纜繩，未料多人被捲進大海。片段顯示現場有一艘潛艇，有消息指是核潛艇平台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180824/bkn-20180824082623947-0824_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180824%2Fbkn-20180824082623947-0824_00952_001.html&d=itMRmcMEBhBK6NMbRZTM%2BP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d8333a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180824/bkn-20180824082623947-0824_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ffd53816e426b3706a9ee7a29b938385e3f4271","tid":792051,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"一班高層走去拉纜繩係咩玩法"},{"pid":"8b67ee144655fa7644b48103c2f1a743b25465ad","tid":792051,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/173031_b870c9455e3f8aeb49cf41c53406761e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F173031_b870c9455e3f8aeb49cf41c53406761e.gif&h=cba8942a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84b59dc6b09049b5b09eb52e4d883653915fa45f","tid":792051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 